ntimeClient.close()`\n308:   - Close data plane client\n309:   - Log cleanup\n310:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n311:   - Verify: Resources cleaned up\n312: \n313: ---\n314: \n315: ## Phase 5: Package Configuration ✓\n316: \n317: - [x] **T5.1** Create `pyproject.toml`\n318:   - Build system: `setuptools>=61.0`, `wheel`\n319:   - Project name: `agentcube-sdk`\n320:   - Version: `0.1.0`\n321:   - Requires Python: `>=3.10`\n322:   - Dependencies: `requests`, `PyJWT>=2.0.0`, `cryptography`\n323:   - Package find: `agentcube*`\n324:   - File: `sdk-python/pyproject.toml`\n325:   - Verify: `pip install .` succeeds\n326: \n327: ---\n328: \n329: ## Phase 6: Unit Tests ✓\n330: \n331: - [x] **T6.1** Test `ControlPlaneClient.create_session()`\n332:   - Mock HTTP session, verify POST request\n333:   - Assert correct URL, body, headers\n334:   - Verify `sessionId` extracted from response\n335:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_control_plane.py`\n336:   - Verify: Session created with correct spec\n337: \n338: - [x] **T6.2** Test `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session()`\n339:   - Test success (200), not found (404), error cases\n340:   - Verify idempotent behavior on 404\n341:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_control_plane.py`\n342:   - Verify: Returns True on 404, False on error\n343: \n344: - [x] **T6.3** Test `ControlPlaneClient` URL resolution\n345:   - Test with arg, env var, missing\n346:   - Verify `ValueError` on missing\n347:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_control_plane.py`\n348:   - Verify: Fallback to env works\n349: \n350: - [x] **T6.4** Test `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient.execute_command()`\n351:   - Mock successful execution\n352:   - Mock non-zero exit code\n353:   - Verify `CommandExecutionError` raised\n354:   - Verify timeout buffer applied\n355:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n356:   - Verify: Raises on error, returns stdout on success\n357: \n358: - [x] **T6.5** Test `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient.run_code()