{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876554963,"sessionID":"ses_285848030ffeoyxjtecM7eKwNE","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7c5d78001RUsomSXtqqfw7u","messageID":"msg_d7a7c35cb001Dn3aFmYP9Nc6q6","sessionID":"ses_285848030ffeoyxjtecM7eKwNE","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_24300d8f44864ccea2d7d862","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md","content":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Package Structure & Exports\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Update `agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeClient` from `agent_runtime`\n  - Update `__all__` to include `\"AgentRuntimeClient\"`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Verify: `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient` works\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Update `agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` from `agent_runtime_data_plane`\n  - Add to `__all__` list\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - Verify: Client imports from `agentcube.clients`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Data Plane Client\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`, dependencies (`requests`, `logging`, `urljoin`)\n  - Define class with `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` constant\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Module structure correct\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.__init__()`\n  - Parameters: `router_url`, `namespace`, `agent_name`, `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n  - Compute `base_url` from `router_url` + `/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n  - Create session with `create_session()`\n  - Initialize logger\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Base URL computed correctly, session initialized\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()`\n  - GET request to `self.base_url`\n  - Timeout: `(connect_timeout, timeout)`\n  - Extract `x-agentcube-session-id` from response headers\n  - Raise `ValueError` if header missing\n  - Return session ID string\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Session ID extracted or ValueError raised\n\n- [ ] **T2.4** Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()`\n  - Parameters: `session_id`, `payload: Dict[str, Any]`, `timeout: Optional[float]`\n  - Set headers: `x-agentcube-session-id`, `Content-Type: application/json`\n  - POST JSON payload to `self.base_url`\n  - Apply timeout: use override or instance default\n  - Return `requests.Response`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Request sent with correct headers and timeout\n\n- [ ] **T2.5** Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.close()`\n  - Call `self.session.close()`\n  - Log cleanup action\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: HTTP session closed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: High-Level Client\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Create `agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeClient`, dependencies (`AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`, `os`, `logging`)\n  - Define class\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Module structure correct\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient.__init__()`\n  - Parameters: `agent_name`, `namespace=\"default\"`, `router_url=None`, `verbose=False`, `session_id=None`, `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`\n  - Store instance attributes\n  - Initialize logger with verbose level\n  - Resolve `router_url` from arg or `ROUTER_URL` env var\n  - Raise `ValueError` if router_url missing\n  - Bootstrap session_id if not provided via `_bootstrap_session_id()`\n  - Create `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Client instantiates, session bootstrapped or reused\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient._bootstrap_session_id()`\n  - Create temporary `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n  - Call `bootstrap_session_id()`\n  - Store result as `self.session_id`\n  - Close temporary client\n  - Return session ID\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Session ID bootstrapped from endpoint\n\n- [ ] **T3.4** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient.__enter__()` and `__exit__()`\n  - `__enter__`: return `self`\n  - `__exit__`: call `self.close()`\n  - Support context manager protocol\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: `with` statement works\n\n- [ ] **T3.5** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()`\n  - Parameters: `payload: Dict[str, Any]`, `timeout: Optional[float] = None`\n  - Check `session_id` is set, raise `ValueError` if not\n  - Call `dp_client.invoke()` with session_id, payload, timeout\n  - Return `response.json()`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Invocation returns parsed JSON\n\n- [ ] **T3.6** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient.close()`\n  - Call `dp_client.close()`\n  - Log cleanup action\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Resources cleaned up\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.__init__()` with explicit session_id\n  - Verify bootstrap NOT called when session_id provided\n  - Verify session_id stored correctly\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Bootstrap skipped\n\n- [ ] **T4.2** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.__init__()` without session_id\n  - Verify bootstrap IS called when session_id is None\n  - Verify bootstrapped session_id stored\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Bootstrap triggered\n\n- [ ] **T4.3** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` router_url resolution\n  - Test with explicit arg\n  - Test with `ROUTER_URL` env var\n  - Test missing both raises `ValueError`\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Fallback chain works\n\n- [ ] **T4.4** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` timeout defaults\n  - Verify `timeout=120` default\n  - Verify `connect_timeout=5.0` default\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Defaults applied\n\n- [ ] **T4.5** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` namespace default\n  - Verify `namespace=\"default\"` when not specified\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Default namespace\n\n- [ ] **T4.6** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` context manager enter\n  - Verify `__enter__` returns `self`\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Context manager works\n\n- [ ] **T4.7** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` context manager exit\n  - Verify `close()` called on normal exit\n  - Verify `close()` called on exception\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Cleanup always happens\n\n- [ ] **T4.8** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()` with payload\n  - Verify `dp_client.invoke()` called with correct params\n  - Verify parsed JSON returned\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Delegation works\n\n- [ ] **T4.9** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()` without session\n  - Verify `ValueError` raised when session_id is None\n  - Verify error message clear\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Protection works\n\n- [ ] **T4.10** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()` with timeout override\n  - Verify timeout param passed to dp_client\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Timeout override works\n\n- [ ] **T4.11** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.close()`\n  - Verify `dp_client.close()` called\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Cleanup delegated\n\n- [ ] **T4.12** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.__init__()` base URL computation\n  - Verify URL format: `{router_url}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: URL computed correctly\n\n- [ ] **T4.13** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER` constant\n  - Verify equals `\"x-agentcube-session-id\"` (lowercase)\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Constant correct\n\n- [ ] **T4.14** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` success\n  - Mock GET response with session header\n  - Verify header value returned\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Session ID extracted\n\n- [ ] **T4.15** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` missing header\n  - Mock GET response without session header\n  - Verify `ValueError` raised with clear message\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Error handling\n\n- [ ] **T4.16** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` request\n  - Verify GET to base_url with timeout tuple\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Request correct\n\n- [ ] **T4.17** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()` POST request\n  - Verify POST to base_url with JSON body\n  - Verify session header set\n  - Verify Content-Type header set\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Request correct\n\n- [ ] **T4.18** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()` timeout handling\n  - Test default timeout from instance\n  - Test timeout override\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Timeout applied correctly\n\n- [ ] **T4.19** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke()` response\n  - Verify `requests.Response` returned\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Response returned\n\n- [ ] **T4.20** Test `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.close()`\n  - Verify `session.close()` called\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: HTTP session closed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Create integration test fixture\n  - Check for `ROUTER_URL` env var\n  - Create `AgentRuntimeClient` instance\n  - Cleanup on teardown\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/integration/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Tests skip if env var missing\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` bootstrap\n  - Create client without session_id\n  - Verify session_id bootstrapped\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/integration/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Bootstrap works live\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Test `AgentRuntimeClient.invoke()`\n  - Invoke with test payload\n  - Verify response not None\n  - Verify response structure\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/integration/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: End-to-end invocation\n\n- [ ] **T5.4** Test `AgentRuntimeClient` context manager\n  - Use `with` statement\n  - Invoke agent\n  - Verify cleanup on exit\n  - File: `sdk-python/tests/integration/test_agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Full lifecycle\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Code Quality\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Add docstrings to `AgentRuntimeClient` class\n  - Document purpose, attributes\n  - Document usage pattern\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: `help()` displays correctly\n\n- [ ] **T6.2** Add docstrings to `AgentRuntimeClient` methods\n  - Document parameters with types\n  - Document return values\n  - Document exceptions\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - Verify: Complete API docs\n\n- [ ] **T6.3** Add docstrings to `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` class\n  - Document purpose, attributes\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: `help()` displays correctly\n\n- [ ] **T6.4** Add docstrings to `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` methods\n  - Document parameters with types\n  - Document return values\n  - Document exceptions\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - Verify: Complete API docs\n\n- [ ] **T6.5** Add type hints to all functions\n  - Use `typing` module for complex types\n  - File: All source files\n  - Verify: mypy passes\n\n- [ ] **T6.6** Run mypy type checking\n  - Command: `mypy sdk-python/agentcube/`\n  - Fix all type errors\n  - Verify: No mypy errors\n\n- [ ] **T6.7** Run ruff/flake8 linting\n  - Command: `ruff check sdk-python/agentcube/`\n  - Fix all lint errors\n  - Verify: No lint errors\n\n- [ ] **T6.8** Run pytest with coverage\n  - Command: `pytest --cov=agentcube sdk-python/tests/`\n  - Verify coverage >= 80%\n  - Verify: All methods tested\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Examples & Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T7.1** Create `examples/agent_runtime_basic.py`\n  - Show `AgentRuntimeClient` with `with` statement\n  - Demonstrate `invoke()`\n  - Show context manager cleanup\n  - File: `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_basic.py`\n  - Verify: Example is runnable\n\n- [ ] **T7.2** Create `examples/agent_runtime_explicit_session.py`\n  - Show providing explicit `session_id`\n  - Demonstrate session reuse\n  - File: `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_explicit_session.py`\n  - Verify: Example is runnable\n\n- [ ] **T7.3** Update `README.md`\n  - Add `AgentRuntimeClient` section\n  - Installation instructions\n  - Quick start examples\n  - API overview\n  - Environment variables\n  - File: `sdk-python/README.md`\n  - Verify: Clear documentation\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. ✅ `AgentRuntimeClient` bootstraps session_id via GET invocation endpoint when not provided\n2. ✅ `AgentRuntimeClient` reuses provided session_id without bootstrap\n3. ✅ Router URL resolves from arg → `ROUTER_URL` env → `ValueError`\n4. ✅ Context manager `__exit__` calls `close()`, cleans up HTTP session\n5. ✅ `invoke()` raises `ValueError` if session_id not initialized\n6. ✅ `invoke()` returns parsed JSON from response\n7. ✅ Per-call timeout override works in `invoke(timeout=60)`\n8. ✅ Timeout defaults: read=120s, connect=5.0s\n9. ✅ Session header uses lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id`\n10. ✅ Base URL computed: `{router_url}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n11. ✅ HTTP session with connection pooling (10/10)\n12. ✅ `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` raises `ValueError` on missing header\n13. ✅ Package installs via `pip install .`\n14. ✅ Imports work: `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient`\n15. ✅ Unit tests cover all clients and error cases (>= 80% coverage)\n16. ✅ Integration tests pass in live environment\n17. ✅ Type hints pass mypy validation\n18. ✅ Code passes ruff/flake8 linting\n19. ✅ Examples provided and runnable\n20. ✅ README documents installation and usage\n\n---\n\n**Notes:**\n- Stage ST-3: Design completed, implementation pending\n- Session header naming: uses lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id` throughout\n- Timeout handling: no buffer needed (unlike CodeInterpreterClient execute_command)\n- Session bootstrap: happens in `__init__` if session_id not provided\n- No control plane involvement (unlike CodeInterpreterClient)\n- Router URL required: no fallback to default, must be provided or in env\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775876554948,"end":1775876554959}}}}
